Name: Eatology Asian
Description: Traditional Asian diet is definitely one of the healthiest diet worldwide. The Asian food culture focuses on achieving a balance of different flavors and foods. It is high in vitamins, minerals, fiber and antioxidants and low in saturated fat. It mostly incorporates vegetables, fruits, nuts and legumes and is low in meat and dairy products. Our chefs and our nutritionist have gathered for you the best flavors from the historical diets of China, Japan, Korea, Thailand and many other countries in the region. Try it and enjoy the food!
